        Heritage Overlays and Property Sales in Brisbane: What Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        What a heritage overlay means for your Brisbane property, how it affects what buyers can do, and how to present it as an asset rather than a constraint when you sell.
